    <summary>Unified CLI for FHIR processing tools</summary>
    <description>RH is a modern, high-performance toolkit for working with HL7 FHIR. This package installs the `rh` command-line interface for FHIR validation, CQL compilation, FHIRPath evaluation, FSH compilation, and more.</description>
